gov.nih.nlm.meme.common
Interface EditorPreferences

All Known Implementing Classes:
EditorPreferences.Default
public interface EditorPreferences

Generically represents information about editors tracked by the system, including their preferences for using the editing interface.

Author:
MEME Group

Nested Class Summary
static class EditorPreferences.Default
          This inner class serves as a default implementation of the EditorPreferences interface.
